Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:00.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,どりゃ～！\Nうお～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:10.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ミフネ）ひけ！　ひけ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:33.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,（カンクロウ）\N一流の傀儡使いのチャクラ糸は→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:36.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,傀儡だけじゃなく\N人も操ることができる。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:42.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが　チャクラ糸を切ってしまえば\N操られてるヤツに害はないじゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:46.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,かたじけない。\N味方を殺めるところであった。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:51.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,傀儡使いには\N傀儡使いの戦い方があるからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:55.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,まっ\N俺が引き受けるしかないじゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:57.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,なあ　チヨバア！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,（チヨバア）カンクロウ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:08.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サソリ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:14.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,わしのしてきたことは\N間違いばかりじゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:19.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃが　ナルトに出会い\N最後に正しいことができた。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:25.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして未来に希望を残し\N死ねたはずじゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:32.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃがな　やはりお前を前にすれば\N後悔の過去を思い出してしまう。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:34.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリよ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:50.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,((サソリ：お父様と　お母様は\Nいつ戻られますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:54.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,うん　もう少し\N先になるらしいのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:57.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,(そうですか…))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:11.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,《チヨバア：わしには　本当のことを\N伝えることができなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:17.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,両親の死を知らせるには\Nサソリは　あまりにも幼すぎた》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,((うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:50.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サソリ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:21.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,《チヨバア：気づいておったのじゃ。\Nサソリは両親の死を…》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,((コムシ：サソリ！　元気してるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:40.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,この前の傀儡も\N評判がよかったって→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,チヨバア様が言ってたぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:46.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺も　いつか　オメエの傀儡ぐらい\Nすげぇ！　って言われる忍に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,（コムシ）おい！　聞いてんのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,お～い　俺ですよ～。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:57.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,コムシが来ましたよ～。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:02.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,おい！　返事しろって！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:08.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:14.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,わ…　わざとじゃないぞ。\N悪かったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:18.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも　俺の扱い\Nもしかして人形以下か？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:22.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,まあ　お前のリアクションに→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,いちいち落ち込んでたら\Nキリがないからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,チヨバア様からの言づてだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,依頼しておいた\N傀儡の納期を早め…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:34.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,（サソリ）烏　黒蟻　山椒魚。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,依頼書どおり　造形完了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:44.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,へ～っ　これが新作か。\Nしかし　ずいぶんと早く…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:47.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,待たせるのは嫌いだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうか…　そうだよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,（コムシ）へ～っ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:03.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,大したもんだな。\Nまるで人の指みたいだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,（サソリ）ふむ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:15.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,あっ…　おっと　忘れるとこだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:18.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,その新作の…\N烏用の毒を　どうするか→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,それも聞いとけって\N言われたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:25.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,希少薬草ばっかじゃん　これ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:33.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,これを調合するってのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:38.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,けど　こりゃ　許可証が必要だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:41.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,よし！　このコムシ様が\N掛け合ってやるからさ→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待っててくれ…。\N待つのは　イヤだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:46.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,だよな。　じゃ　行こうぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:58.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,（コムシ）コムシです。\Nなんじゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:02.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,おお　伝言　伝えて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:09.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,チヨバア様\Nサソリから　お願いがあるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんじゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:20.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,フム…　配合比率がわからんと\Nなんとも言えないが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:32.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,おぬしのことじゃ。　問題なかろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,医薬部には　話をつけておく。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:41.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,わしは研究の続きがあるゆえ\Nもう下がれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:44.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,（コムシ）あ～あ　サソリは　いいよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:48.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,その歳で立派に\N里の役に立ってるんだもんな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:51.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,チヨバア様も鼻が高いだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,聞いてるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:58.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,チヨバア様は　いつも\Nお前のこと気にかけてるんだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺もさ　早くお前の傀儡みたいに→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:04.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,一人前の忍として認められたいぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:08.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,うちの親は　いつも\N俺を　ガキ扱いなんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,忍に向いてないって。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:14.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも　今度\N国境の警備を任されたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:17.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,そりゃ　ただの警備だけど\Nそこで手柄を立てれば…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:20.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,コムシ！\Nこんな時間まで何してるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,心配するでしょ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,ちょっ…\Nやめてくれよ　かっこわるい。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:26.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,これから\N俺だって警備の任務に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,任務なんて断ったっていいのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,母さんが\N一生　面倒みてあげるから。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,（コムシ）だから　やめろって！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,サンキュー！　サソリ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:48.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,聞いたぞ。　任務で\Nケガをしたというではないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:53.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヘマをしちまって。　でもね…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんと！　傀儡の腕を…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:59.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,それだけじゃないんですよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:01.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヘヘヘ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:04.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,前より強くなった気分です。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,それに　本当　ピッタリなんだよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:10.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,もともと\N俺の体だったみたいなんすよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,（コムシ）ぐわ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:28.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,仕込みの毒を　自ら食らうとは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:34.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,（コムシ）チヨバア様\Nアイツは…　アイツは悪くねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:38.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,悪いのは　ドジを踏んだ俺…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぐわ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:44.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,え～い！　サソリは！？\N毒の配合比率は　まだか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:47.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,うわ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:59.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,治してください　治してください\N治してください　治して！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:03.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,右腕だって\Nあなたが　つけたんでしょ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,なら　左腕も…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:11.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,足も　体も…\N魂だって　治せるはずでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:17.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,(返して！　私のコムシを\N治して　返してください！！))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,《痛ましい事故であった。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:27.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,コムシは　わしとサソリを\Nよく　つないでくれた。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,それだけではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:35.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリにとっても　唯一といっていい\N友じゃったのに…》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,((サソリの近況は　どうじゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:41.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,ふだんと変わりありませんよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,最近は\N細かい傀儡のパーツを作ってますね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,(これが　本当に人の手みたいで…))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:56.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,((ん！？　なんじゃ？　まさか…。\N偶然のはずじゃが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:12:00.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,何かが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,《思い過ごしで\Nあってくれればよいが…》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,（サソリ）待たせるのは嫌いだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:21.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,目測では　もう少し\N成長するかと思ったが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリ！　何をしておる！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぎりぎり　規格のサイズに収まったか。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,コムシじゃと！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:04.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,(（サソリ）依頼どおり　造形完了))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:20.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,《わしは　あやつが最もつらいとき\Nそばにいてやれなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:24.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,愛情を最も欲したときにそばに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:28.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや　本当は　あやつのもとから\N口実をつくって逃げていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:32.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,わしが　あやつを\Nあのように歪めてしまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:35.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,すまぬ。　よみがえった死人が→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:39.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,傀儡になったお前に\N謝ったところで今更じゃが…》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,技のキレは　さすがじゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが　闘志が宿ってねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:14.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,やっぱ　傀儡使いが操られてちゃ\Nダメってことじゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:18.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,フン　若造が　わかったようなことを。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:22.18,japanese,,0,0,0,,この穢土転生という術を\Nあなどるでないぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:24.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,術者が本気になれば…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:29.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,言うとるそばから…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:40.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,裏白秘技　十機偽松の集！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,えっ　ワイヤーじゃと？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,な…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:17.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリも　このサソリの父と母も→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺が回収して直したんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:38.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,((サクラ：アイツは　サソリは言ってました。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:43.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,自分は人形に\Nなりきれなかった人間だって。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:47.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,生身の核を持つ\N不完全な傀儡だって。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,傀儡になった\Nお父さんと　お母さんに→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:53.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,近づきたかったんですかね。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,魂のない人形に\Nなりたいだなんて。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:16:02.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうかもな。　だけどよ→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:07.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺には　この傀儡\Nサソリの父と母に宿る魂を感じるぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:10.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリのヤツも\Nそれを感じたと信じたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:15.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,チヨバア様が言ってました。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:18.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,お父さんとお母さんの\N最後の攻撃は→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:23.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリに見えていた。　それでも\Nなぜかかわさなかったって。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:32.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ああ　伝わったんだろうな。\N父と母の魂の叫びってヤツがよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,確かに　俺は若造じゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:37.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが\Nチャクラ糸を通して伝わってくる→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:42.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,アンタの後悔や悲しみに\N気づかないほど鈍感じゃないぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.18,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぬけぬけと思ったことを\N言いおって。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:47.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,だから　若造というんじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:51.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,償いたくても償えないこともある。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,ましてや　わしは死人じゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:56.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうすることもできんわい。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:59.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺は　サソリに託されたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:06.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,((サソリ：父と母の傀儡も\Nお前に託す))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリが　おぬしに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:12.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,（カンクロウ）さすが\Nサソリが作った傀儡だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,仕込みはもちろん\N指先に至るまで→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:18.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,繊細に作りこまれている。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,《こやつもサソリ同様→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:23.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,傀儡への並々ならぬ愛情を\N持っておるのか》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:27.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,この２人には　サソリの魂が宿ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:29.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして　その思いが→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:32.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,傀儡に父と母の魂をも宿らせた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:38.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,少なくともサソリは\Nそう感じていたはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,傀儡に魂じゃと？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,それだけじゃないぜ　チヨバア。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,父と母を操演したアンタの思いも→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:49.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,魂となって\Nこの２人に宿ってるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリは　それをわかっていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:55.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,すべてをひっくるめて\Nサソリは俺に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:59.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや　未来の忍世界に託したのさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:01.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,それを受け継いで\N伝えていくのも→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺たちの役目ってわけじゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:05.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,たしかに　俺は　若造で→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,アンタから見れば\N他人かもしれねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが弟は　我愛羅は→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,アンタの魂を貰って\N生き返ったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:17.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,とても他人とは　思えねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:20.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,それに\Nチャクラ糸を通して感じるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:24.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリと父と母　家族の思いが→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,魂の声がこう言っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,チヨバアを止めてやってくれってな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,家族…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:39.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,((母さん！　たかが\N家族の記念写真なんだから→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:41.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんなに強情にならなくても。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:44.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,バカもん。\N忍んでこその忍じゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:47.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんなものを撮って\N写真立てに飾り→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,ホームパーチーなんぞで\N「よいお写真ですね」なんて→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:52.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,言われるのは\Nまっぴらごめんじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,そ　そこまでは　言ってませんけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:57.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,言ってるも同然じゃわい。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:59.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,（サソリ）チヨバア様。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:01.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,写真　一緒に撮るの嫌なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:09.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや　そういうことを\N言っておるのでは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:11.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう　しようがないな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,おおう…　何をする！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:24.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,む～。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:26.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ああ！！))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:45.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,それにしても　よき操演者に\N引き継がれたものよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:05.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,チヨバア！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:12.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,な～んてな。　リアル死んだふり。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:17.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,ゲヘ　ゲヘ　ゲヘヘヘヘヘ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:20.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,さて　サソリが父と母を→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,置き土産として\N置いていったのに→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:26.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,わしが何も残さんわけには\Nいかんのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,今のわしが\Nお前に残してやれるのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,傀儡の奥義くらいのもんじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:33.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,その身をもって学ぶがよい。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:38.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,（カンクロウ）ちょっと待っ…。\N（チヨバア）白秘技奥義　夢幻の集！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:40.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,マジやべえじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,（チヨバア）アッハッハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:49.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,（カンクロウ）ガキの頃　あんなに\N修業つけてくれって→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,せがんだのに　里の未来なんか\Nどうでもいいって→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:53.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,相手にしてくれなかったじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,（チヨバア）わしも若かったからのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:57.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,（カンクロウ）十分　ババアだったじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:02.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,（チヨバア）アーハッハッハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:52.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,皆様　お変わりございませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.75,0:22:55.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,美空ひばりです。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:23:00.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,では最後まで\Nごゆっくりお楽しみください。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:03.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,（宮本）『木曜８時のコンサート。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:06.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,名曲！　にっぽんの歌』\N２時間スペシャル。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.41,0:01:35.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Soul Living{\i0}\N{\i1}Inside the Puppet{\i0}\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:09.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat… Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:33.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chakra Threads of world-class\NPuppet Masters can control humans
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:36.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as their puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:41.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But once the Chakra Thread is cut,\Nthere's no harm to the human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:43.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm indebted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:46.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to slay an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:50.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a special way to fight\Nbetween Puppet Users.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:54.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the only one here\Nwho can do this…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:56.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Granny Chiyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:02:59.16,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Kankuro…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasori…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:14.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I erred in everything I did…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But after meeting Naruto,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:19.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was able to do{\i0}\N{\i1}the right thing in the end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I died,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:24.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}leaving some hope{\i0}\N{\i1}for a bright future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:26.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:29.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I stand before you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:33.62,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't help{\i0}\N{\i1}but regret the past… Sasori…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:47.99,english,,0000,0000,0000,,When are mother and father\Ncoming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:54.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they'll be gone a little bit longer…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:57.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:10.99,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't bring myself{\i0}\N{\i1}to tell him the truth…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:17.16,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasori was too young to know{\i0}\N{\i1}about his parents' deaths…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:20.66,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasori had already figured out,{\i0}\N{\i1}that his parents were dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori! How've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:33.66,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:42.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Chiyo said\Nyour last puppet was a huge hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Some day, I want to be\Na shinobi like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,where everyone praises my puppets…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.62,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.12,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:56.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Komushi has come\Nto see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:02.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, I didn't mean it.\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:18.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're treating me worse\Nthan a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:23.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, I might as well wait\Nuntil hell freezes over
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:25.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,to get a response from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from Granny Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants the puppets\Nshe ordered sooner…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Crow, Black Ant and Salamander…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:40.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything she requested is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:43.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so these are your new creations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:44.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was quick…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like to keep people waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:49.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:00.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey… That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:02.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,They look so human!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,About your new creation…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.62,english,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked me to inquire about\Nthe poison for the Crow puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:30.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all rare medicinal plants!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna make\Na mixture out of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to require permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:42.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Komushi, will negotiate this!\NSo give me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:46.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not. Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Komushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:02.16,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… Did you relay my message…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Chiyo, Sasori has a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:19.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much I can say
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.99,english,,0000,0000,0000,,without knowing the blending ratio\Nof the mixture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:32.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But since this is coming from you,\NI have no issues with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clear it with\Nthe Pharmaceuticals Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:40.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the middle of research,\Nso you may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you've got it made, Sasori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:47.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still young, but you're already\Ncontributing to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Chiyo must be\Nso proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:54.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:58.12,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Chiyo is always\Nworried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:02.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to be acknowledged\Nas a full-fledged shinobi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,just like your puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:08.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My own parents still treat me\Nlike a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,They tell me I'm not suited\Nto being a shinobi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:14.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time,\NI was assigned to border security.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just guard duty,\Nbut if I can prove myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:18.99,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Komushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing\Nat this hour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.62,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait… Cut it out,\Nyou're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.99,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be assigned border\Nsecurity missions from now on…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You can turn down things\Nlike missions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:31.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of you\Nfor the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:33.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sasori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you were injured on duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:52.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:56.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's…a puppet arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel stronger than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And it fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it's always been\Na part of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you ingest\Nyour own poison?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Chiyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:34.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's… He's not to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:38.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one…who messed up…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Sasori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have the blending ratio\Nof the poison yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Please heal him…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Please heal him…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.66,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Heal him! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.99,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You attached his right arm too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:05.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then his left arm can be…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:08.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,His legs, his body…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:11.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even heal his soul, can't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:13.16,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:17.12,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Heal my Komushi and\Ngive him back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a painful accident.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.62,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Komushi was my link to Sasori…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only that…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:34.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was Sasori's only friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:38.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,How has Sasori been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:44.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been working on\Nsmall puppet parts recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And they look like\Nreal human hands…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:55.74,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. It has to be a coincidence…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:57.99,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But something is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:06.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope my fears are ungrounded!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like to make people wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:18.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there'd be\Na little more progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:24.16,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.99,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You barely got it to\Nthe standard size…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:28.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:38.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Komushi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As requested…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:05.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The model is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:21.24,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wasn't able to be at his side{\i0}\N{\i1}when he was suffering the most.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:24.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When he desperately needed love…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:29.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I made excuses and{\i0}\N{\i1}distanced myself from him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the one who distorted him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:33.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Much good it does at this point…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:39.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An apology from a reanimated corpse{\i0}\N{\i1}to the puppet that you are now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:08.14,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Your technique is as sharp as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have any fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:14.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Puppet Masters aren't good\Nat being a puppet, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:18.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Inexperienced ones shouldn't act\Nas if they know….
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:22.02,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make light of\Nthe Reanimation Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:24.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If the user of the jutsu gets serious…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:28.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, speak of the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.68,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Secret White Technique…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.89,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Esematsu's Ten Puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:57.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wires?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.06,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:17.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori…as well as\NSasori's Mother and Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.85,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I recovered and repaired them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:38.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori told me…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:42.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,that he was a human\Nwho wasn't able to become a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:46.68,english,,0000,0000,0000,,An incomplete puppet with\Na core that was living flesh…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:50.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he wanted to\Nbe closer to his parents
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:52.02,english,,0000,0000,0000,,who had become puppets?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,How could anyone want to\Nbecome a puppet without a soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.52,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Possibly…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.06,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:05.52,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense the souls of\NSasori's mother and father
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.14,english,,0000,0000,0000,,inside these puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:10.39,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to believe that\NSasori felt it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:15.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Chiyo said…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:19.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,that Sasori was able to see\Nhis mother and father's final attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:23.68,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason,\Nhe didn't counter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:27.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… It must've reached him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:30.89,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The cry of his parents' souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit I'm inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not so ignorant\Nthat I couldn't feel
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:42.06,english,,0000,0000,0000,,your regret and sadness\Nthrough your Chakra Threads.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:45.06,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You say the first thing\Nthat pops up in your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.14,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're inexperienced!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:51.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things one wants\Nto atone for, but can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:59.06,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori entrusted me…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:05.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I entrust you with the Father{\i0}\N{\i1}and Mother puppets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:09.06,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori entrusted you…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Puppets that only Sasori could create.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:16.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Their workings are so delicate…\Nall the way down to the fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:21.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he shares a love and{\i0}\N{\i1}passion for puppets,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just like Sasori did?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.89,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori's soul dwells in\Nthese two puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:32.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And his love instilled the souls\Nof his parents in them too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori, at least, was able to feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Puppets with souls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all, Granny Chiyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:45.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The love you gave to\Nhis Father and Mother puppets
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,became a part of their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:49.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.39,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori was aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And he gave them all to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, he entrusted them to me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:58.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,for future generations\Nof the shinobi world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:03.14,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Passing it on is our duty too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori did that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:09.56,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'm inexperienced and\Nin your eyes, a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But my kid brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:14.14,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaara received your soul\Nand came back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.14,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm not a stranger at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:20.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can sense it through\Nthe Chakra Threads.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:22.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasori and his mother and father…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The family's thoughts, their love…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:26.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Their souls are saying…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:29.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please stop Granny Chiyo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Family…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:36.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:40.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a family portrait.\NDon't be so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:44.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! The meaning of\Nthe word "shinobi" is to be stealthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.14,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not take a photo,\Nto be put up as decoration